    <h2>
      <a href="/episodes/14-performing-calculations-on-models">Performing Calculations on Models</a>
      
    </h2>
    <div class="description">
      Did you know ActiveRecord provides class methods for performing calculations on models? You can even use these methods through associations.
      <span class="stats">(2 minutes)</span>
    </div>
    <div class="watch">
